overview: Bree's College Daze is back! This time she's attending an all girl prep school for the summer and on a mission to help one of her new friends gain confidence in meeting boys. It's a college movie you won't want to miss! The sex action makes this one of the best of Bree's College Daze series. Bree leads a cast of the hottest new young girls hell bent on higher learning!
title: Bree's College Daze 3
